@congUoM the package name in
https://github.com/congUoM/Microscopes.jl/blob/841aa69f8a78d6636d7fc24bb56fea120ebba45a/Project.toml#L1 should be `Microscopes`, not `Microscopes.jl`.  Also, the package must have [compat bounds](https://julialang.github.io/Pkg.jl/v1/compatibility/) for all depending packages and including Julia itself, see https://github.com/JuliaRegistries/General/blob/48a652c927133c3841f91cc7d8fc88d56472e0cb/README.md#automatic-merging-of-pull-requests.

I'm going to close the pull request because the name is wrong anyway.
